{"id":273301,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-17名长沙上访维权人士在京控告非法拘禁遭/","date":"2013-01-07T13:46:08Z","modified":"2013-01-07T13:46:08Z","title":"维权网 | 17名长沙上访维权人士在京控告非法拘禁遭推诿（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）本网此前报道，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月，长沙吴莎、李香等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>名上访维权人士在北京旅游时被非法绑架回长沙，刘华、李颂明、曾武、邓生记等人因为去接</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>人而被以危害安全罪逮捕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>点多，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>位去年在京旅游被绑架的人员，到北京市公安局举报天安门警察非法拘禁，非法限制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>人的人身自由，并要求立案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>接待的警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">000308</span><span>的工作人员对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>人说，他会将情况转交天安门分局纪委。上访维权人士质疑说，为什么要转交，北京市公安局难道不管警察吗？警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">000084</span><span>的工作人员要大家去找天安门分局，而投诉者们认为：哪有犯罪分子自己查自己的道理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道请见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.jp/2012/12/blog-post_4129.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.jp/2012/12/blog-post_4129.html</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qrtoguPVVig/UOpygW_7lZI/AAAAAAAAYVY/sebXju8Wur8/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qrtoguPVVig/UOpygW_7lZI/AAAAAAAAYVY/sebXju8Wur8/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MCjpm4vLjIk/UOpyfqIiNYI/AAAAAAAAYVU/H4ljnfUmbdU/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" sr